'''''Dragon Magazine'' 157''' was the 157th issue of [[Dragon (magazine)|''Dragon Magazine'']]. It was published by [[TSR, Inc.]] in [[May]] [[1990]].

This issue features the unlicensed ''[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]'' article "[[For the Greater Good]]," written by [[Carl Sargent]] with artwork by [[Stephen Schwartz]].

